===Voordelen===
*Traffic jams unlikely.
*Can handle 3 trains at a time.
*Low construction cost.
*Small area.
*Split before merge.
*Deadlock free.
*easier to handle diversion traffic

===Nadelen===
*Main line trains must slow down to climb a slope.
*Sharp turns reduces train speed.

